<section class="hero"><div class="hero-copy"><div class="mission-pill"><span></span>Mission Control for telegram first teams</div><h1><span>Your team runs on telegram</span><br><strong>Now run it like a system</strong></h1><p>Turns your Telegram chaos into one clean control center.<br>Tracks every single ask, pending action, and daily number.<br>Zero migration required no new app to learn.</p><div class="hero-actions"><a class="button button-primary" href="/signup"><span>➤</span>Add tegsi to your group</a><a class="button button-light" href="#products">Request a demo <span>›</span></a></div></div><div class="hero-orbit"><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>
